title: Winners of the Fantasy Offseason | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
This offseason has given some players a new outlook on their fantasy future. We highlight the fantasy players whose 2020 outlook saw the biggest boost after free agency and the NFL draft. 
Host: Danny Kelly and Craig Horlbeck
